Acked-by: Daniel Stone <daniels@collabora.com>
Signed-off-by: Thierry Reding <treding@nvidia.com>
Link: https://patchwork.freedesktop.org/patch/msgid/20210610111236.3814211-1-thierry.reding@gmail.com

